title: Top 10 Judas Priest
description:
In my opinion, the 10 best songs by Judas Priest.

1. The Green Manalishi (With The Two-Pronged Crown)
2. Screaming For Vengeance
3. The Sentinel
4. Diamonds And Rust (So what, it&#039;s a cover. Still a great song)
5. Painkiller
6. Electric Eye
7. Sinner
8. The Ripper
9. Tyrant
10. Rock Forever

Yeah, I know there are some songs that are better than Sinner or Rock Forever. But I&#039;m trying to get my friend to open up to Judas Priest and stop his bitching about me listening to it, and I believe these are the best songs to do that.
